{"tid":1191964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首行程","createTime":"2019-06-08T07:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:46:37.000Z","uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f116c90664d89276503ae5c371b1798f459e8233","tid":1191964,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"HK01注意<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/338127/政壇諸事町-6-9反修例遊行-林鄭月娥日程滿滿-遠至橋咀島\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F338127%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%A3%87%E8%AB%B8%E4%BA%8B%E7%94%BA-6-9%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E6%97%A5%E7%A8%8B%E6%BB%BF%E6%BB%BF-%E9%81%A0%E8%87%B3%E6%A9%8B%E5%92%80%E5%B3%B6&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8zvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=238b2ead\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/338127/政壇諸事町-6-9反修例遊行-林鄭月娥日程滿滿-遠至橋咀島</a><br />\n<blockquote>行政長官林鄭月娥公務繁忙，上任後除了馬不停蹄地外訪外，出席本港的公開活動亦是不遺餘力。她本周日由早上到傍晚，將會出席三場公開活動，包括早上到西貢橋島出席「重建橋咀碼頭」啟用典禮，中午到科學園出席港科院活動，傍晚就到海洋公園，與中聯辦主任王志民出席新家園主辦的「四海一家」授旗禮，行程可謂相當豐富。<br />\n </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n科學園活動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tf1Cppg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTf1Cppg.png&h=a47017a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對條例有疑問 體力又差既人 可以選擇去親身問下特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇清有另外兩個活動既資料可以補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}